{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505230/extras/eng_save_everyone_2.jpg?t=1733128936\" /><br>Pathologic 2 is a narrative-driven dramatic thriller about fighting a deadly outbreak in a secluded rural town. The town is dying. Face the realities of a collapsing society as you make difficult choices in seemingly lose-lose situations. The plague isn\u2019t just a disease. You can\u2019t save everyone.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505230/extras/pathologic_main_gif.png?t=1733128936\" /><br><br>The plague is devouring the town. The chief local healer is dead, and you are now to take his place. You\u2019ll have to look for unexpected allies. The local kids are hiding something. Try playing by their rules. <br><br>You only have 12 days.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505230/extras/feachers_en.jpg?t=1733128936\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>12 days in an odd town ravaged by a deadly disease.<br></li><li>Time is of the essence: if you don\u2019t manage it carefully, it\u2019ll simply run out. You\u2019ll have to choose how to spend the priceless minutes you have.<br></li><li>Survival thriller. You\u2019ll have to manage your bodily functions, offsetting hunger, thirst, exhaustion, and so on. It doesn\u2019t boil down to scavenging resources. Surviving on your own is hard; you\u2019ll have to win over allies.<br></li><li>An uphill battle. Managing your bodily parameters may seem bearable at first, and as time goes by, it becomes harder and harder. Your own body is only waiting for an opportunity to give up and betray you. Things are changing from bad to worse and the odds are stacked against you.<br></li><li>A duel with an enemy you can\u2019t kill. Your main foe is the plague itself, an incorporeal and malevolent entity that you have to defeat\u2026 without having the means to. It\u2019s more powerful and more treacherous than you can imagine.<br></li><li>Loot, murder, mug, steal, barter, beg\u2026 or don\u2019t. You need resources to survive, and it\u2019s up to you how to obtain them.<br></li><li>The fights are short, ungraceful, and vicious. They\u2019re not always lethal though. Many people\u2014yourself included\u2014would prefer to exchange their wallet for their life.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"On the Run","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/2f57b487a1f82f820216f379b10e23093a25e9fc.jpg"},{"name":"In Kind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/85a655c0c32e60608850f42dbac7af0b41c8494a.jpg"},{"name":"Carpetbagger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/c86277a7b66e715c45278c4858fc8b2d38330d46.jpg"},{"name":"Fate No More","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/5f3a05888ec6acf2f90d2aff44e26150df1baf36.jpg"},{"name":"Heavenly Train","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/8ba3863d61fc63cb76316dc8b57011bcf44344f7.jpg"},{"name":"We're Only Looking","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/b1ba95f1028e34d8a9ba6ba994d9c88367c07dca.jpg"},{"name":"Rotten Tooth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/8e2735925191604fc15cc387c8a1108b3450c0a7.jpg"},{"name":"Another Sky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/3cbc4896f691cfa096aa63254d61e1b8f1d479f4.jpg"},{"name":"Farewell","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/ef38b74ce491d3e94258b84232f8266ffcc15998.jpg"},{"name":"Dream On","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/505230/75137782d1f0d81d8efa9e2dc226e55f1288f514.jpg"}